@FieldOrder({"dwInDatagrams","dwNoPorts","dwInErrors","dwOutDatagrams","dwNumAddrs"})
public static class IPHlpAPI.MIB_UDPSTATS

The MIB_UDPSTATS structure contains statistics for the User Datagram Protocol (UDP) running on the local computer.
